@startuml PLI_Analysis_Pipeline

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam ArrowThickness 2
skinparam RoundCorner 10

skinparam activity {
    BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
    BorderColor #2C5282
    FontColor #1A365D
    DiamondBackgroundColor #FED7AA
    DiamondBorderColor #C05621
}

skinparam partition {
    BackgroundColor #F7FAFC
    BorderColor #4A5568
    FontColor #2D3748
    FontSize 14
    FontStyle bold
}

skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FFFBEB
    BorderColor #D69E2E
    FontSize 10
}

title **PLI Network Analysis Pipeline**\nPhase Lag Index Statistical Analysis Workflow

|#E6F3FF|Data Preprocessing|
start
:**Load Raw Data**\n//Excel file with PLI values//;

:**Filter Dataset**;
note right
  **Selection Criteria:**
  - Groups (Chiro, Control)
  - Sessions (Pre, Post, Post4W)
  - Networks (DMN, SN, CEN)
  - Frequency Bands (Alpha, Beta)
end note

:**Calculate Baseline**\n//Mean PLI from Pre session//\n//per participant/network/band//;

:**Exclude Pre Session**\nfrom Main Analysis;

|#E6FFED|Statistical Analysis|
:**Iterate Over**\nNetwork x Frequency Band;

partition "**Linear Mixed-Effects Model**" {
    :**Define Model**;
    note right
      **Model Specification:**
      DV: MeanPLI
      Fixed: Group + Session +
             Group x Session +
             Baseline (covariate)
      Random: Participant (intercept)
    end note

    :**Fit Model**\n//LBFGS optimization//;

    :**Evaluate Fixed Effects**\n//Main effects & interactions//;
}

|#FFF5E6|Post-Hoc Analysis|
fork
    :**Between-Group**\n**Contrasts**;
    note right
      Independent t-tests
      comparing groups
      at each session
    end note
fork again
    :**Within-Group**\n**Contrasts**;
    note left
      Independent t-tests
      comparing sessions
      within each group
    end note
end fork

:**Apply Significance**\n**Threshold** (p < 0.05);

|#F5E6FF|Visualization & Reporting|
fork
    :**Generate Line Plots**;
    note right
      - Mean PLI per group/session
      - Error bars (SE)
      - Significance markers
        (* p<.05, ** p<.01, *** p<.001)
    end note
fork again
    :**Export to Excel**;
    note left
      - Fixed effects estimates
      - P-values
      - Post-hoc contrasts
    end note
end fork

:**Create Combined**\n**Grid Figure**;

:**Save All Outputs**;

stop

footer Methods: pandas, numpy, statsmodels, scipy | Visualization: matplotlib

@enduml
